; Regression test for issue #616: bal --amount-data uses wrong date
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/616
;
; Bug: bal --amount-data outputs the period-end date for all account entries
; instead of the date of the latest posting to each account.
; Fix: account_t now resolves "date" to the latest posting date.

2024/01/01 First Expense
    Expenses:Food          $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/06/15 Second Expense
    Expenses:Food          $20.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --amount-data -e 2025/01/01 Expenses
2024-06-15 30
end test
